---
description: Create rotating PWA backups after every code change
alwaysApply: true
---

# Rotating Backups (Required)

- After every code-edit step, run:
  - `powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File "scripts/rotate-pwa-backup.ps1"`
- Keep exactly 15 rotating slots:
  - `PWA_backup_slot_01.zip` ... `PWA_backup_slot_15.zip`
  - Slot 16 overwrites slot 01.
- If backup command fails, stop and report the error before continuing.
